━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

The Prop:
- A simple, modern white powder-coated metal rack or shelf
- Clean geometry
- No decorative styling

Arrangement:

Hanging Item:
- The selected merch item is either:
  - hanging on a hanger
  - casually draped over the rack
- Texture must be clearly readable (wool, felt, cotton, knit)

Stacked Items:
- On the rack shelves, stack multiple units of the brand’s core product
- Arrangement options:
  - neat vertical stack
  - pyramid composition
  - orderly row
- Quantity suggests abundance, not clutter

Background:
- Hand-painted canvas backdrop
- Visible brush strokes and surface texture
- Color = chosen deep background tone
- Studio imperfection is intentional and premium

